<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Informational message: Elevated error rates for SQS>
We are currently investigating elevated error rates for SQS in the US-EAST-1 Region.

<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Service is operating normally: [RESOLVED] Elevated error rates for SQS>
Between 7:38 AM and 9:18 AM PDT, we experienced elevated API error rates and connection failures in the US-EAST-1 Region. The issue has been resolved and the service is operating normally.
